-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-25/israel-opportunity-heads-for-biggest-3-month-surge-on-buy-rating.html
Israel Opportunity Energy Resources
LP (ISOPL)  poised for the biggest gain in more than three months after
Clal Finance Batucha Brokerage Ltd. started coverage of the oil
and gas explorer with a buy rating and a price estimate of 0.38
shekels.  The  shares  advanced 7.3 percent, the most since March 15,
to 0.234 shekel, at 10:54 a.m. in Tel Aviv.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
 ssolomon22@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
